channel.title: How do i uninstall guildwars
channel.description:
How do i uninstall guildwars, There is no uninstall icon, and there is not an option for it in "Add and Remove Programs". So how do i remove it.
Situation: I run on a SHITTY 30GB HD i have 511MB and i am in the middle of download Jackass 2 off of iTunes and i don't have enough space. i had to take the seriously painful risk of uninstalling photoshop and that good shit.

item.title: How do i uninstall guildwars
item.dc:creator: @tL tL
item.description:
@tL wrote:

…Delete it from Program files. You will get all your HDD space back that was used by that program.
